What to Expect

Each visit lasts around 2 hours 45 minutes, including:

A guided distillery tour (free)
Optional warehouse tasting hosted by our founder, Annabel, featuring never before tasted casks (£35)
Time to explore the site and enjoy entertainment and food before your return journey

We’re running four sessions across the day, each with limited capacity.



